'''Fellowship of Fans''' is a community of [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] fans who are often first to release information about ''[[The Rings of Power]]'' and ''[[The War of the Rohirrim]]'' adaptations. They are active on various social sites such as Reddit, Twitter, YouTube and Discord.<ref>{{webcite|author=|articleurl=https://fellowshipoffans.com/about/||articlename=About Page|dated=|website=[https://fellowshipoffans.com Fellowship of Fans]|accessed=June 11th, 2023}}</ref>
